64
00:09:26,221 --> 00:09:30,022
<font color="yellow">Do you know what that is?</font>

65
00:09:31,621 --> 00:09:35,221
<font color="yellow">It's your parentage.</font>

66
00:09:35,822 --> 00:09:40,322
<font color="yellow">A parent who is affluent
