78
00:10:34,721 --> 00:10:36,221
<font color="yellow">Do you understand?</font>

79
00:10:38,522 --> 00:10:40,621
<font color="yellow">Y-y-y-yes!</font>

80
00:10:56,721 --> 00:11:02,022
<font color="yellow">Heed my words. If you didn't
understand what I told you today</font>

81
00:11:02,022 --> 00:11:07,422
<font color="yellow">your mother will really
be in there next time.</font>

82
00:12:55,822 --> 00:12:57,422
