136
00:20:38,422 --> 00:20:41,821
<font color="yellow">B-b-begone... begone, you foul creature!</font>

137
00:20:46,019 --> 00:20:51,182
<font color="yellow">Older Brother! Are you regaining
consciousness? It's me, Yeon Hui!</font>

138
00:21:02,726 --> 00:21:07,090
<font color="yellow">B-b-begone... begone, you foul creature!</font>

139
00:21:07,721 --> 00:21:09,622
