143
00:21:38,221 --> 00:21:43,821
<font color="yellow">I'm telling you, I want to live!</font>

144
00:21:43,821 --> 00:21:49,021
<font color="yellow">Let's take our leave, Yeon Hui.
Come on, let's go.</font>

145
00:21:56,622 --> 00:22:01,021
<font color="yellow">You insolent wench.
How dare you come here!</font>

146
00:22:01,021 --> 00:22:02,321
<font color="yellow">Mother.</font>

147
00:22:04,721 --> 00:22:09,422
<font color="yellow">Poong Yeon.
