152
00:22:25,221 --> 00:22:28,922
<font color="yellow">You never should have been born.</font>

153
00:22:28,922 --> 00:22:33,122
<font color="yellow">You should never have
come into this world!</font>

154
00:22:38,321 --> 00:22:46,021
<font color="yellow">I'll beg you on my knees, like this.
