158
00:23:37,021 --> 00:23:38,622
<font color="yellow">Yes, sir.</font>

159
00:23:59,721 --> 00:24:04,122
<font color="yellow">Let's go, Yeon Hui.
Come on.</font>

160
00:24:07,821 --> 00:24:18,122
<font color="yellow">Monk. How can I get to Chungbing Temple?</font>

161
00:24:22,622 --> 00:24:29,321
<font color="yellow">I'll go there.
