162
00:24:30,021 --> 00:24:37,821
<font color="yellow">So please, save my older brother.</font>

163
00:24:47,922 --> 00:24:53,622
<font color="yellow">Sir, we cannot delay this any longer.</font>

164
00:24:55,321 --> 00:25:02,122
<font color="yellow">Sir. A person from the palace
